            <h2 class="title"><a href="/node/113">Cultural Communication Training for Law Enforcement Officers</a></h2>
          
  <div class="content"><p>Module 1 (Group of 12 or less in attendance)<br /><br />
Training: 2 hours (could run longer if participants need more time)</p>
<h2>Introduction</h2>
<ol>
<li>Define effective communication</li>
<li>Discuss why differences are important</li>
<li>Talk about the commonalities</li>
<li>What is the positive outcome of learning to communicate with different cultures</li>
</ol>
<h2>Conversations</h2>
<ol>
<li>"Cultural Hearing"...what does this mean?</li>
<li>What did you say? What was actually heard? (role play)</li>
<li>How different cultures analyze words</li>
</ol></div>
